    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/746020/extras/855ddd0ef629b73d024c4b028079deb0.avif?t=1729003715\" width=520 height=160 /></span><br>This game was re-released in October 2019 with Version 2.0. We increased the story and dialogue from 15.000 to 40.000 words and added alot more content to the game.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Update</h2>Please notice: game was last updated to Version 2.0.2 on 25th October 2019.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Check out the new demo</h2>The demo includes the first chapter of the game, the savefiles are fully compatible with the full version.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Main Characters</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/746020/extras/bed4f5a6868ba27354becde4f45512a1.avif?t=1729003715\" width=520 height=224 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story</h2>Barry and his friends Arlene and Nellie decide to visit the Pit of Evil, the place where they lost their friend Fynn. While spending the night in a tent, things take an unexpected turn. The group gets seperated, while Barry suffers the same fate as Fynn, falling into the Pit of Evil.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Twisted Story with mystery elements<br></li><li>Characters that hold deep connections to each other<br></li><li>Fast-Paced ATB System (Active Time Battle)<br></li><li>On map encounters (Chrono Engine)<br></li><li>Dungeons using puzzle elements<br></li><li>Dramatic cut-scenes, including flashbacks<br></li><li>Challenging boss fights<br></li><li>Interactive world map and journal system</li></ul>",
